ve to be created, suggesting that some approximate\nmethods currently used for galaxy surveys will be inadequate for future weak\nlensing surveys.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 Mar 2015 16:54:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-30"}
